1
00:02:27,510 --> 00:02:29,950
[The Tower of Whispers]

2
00:02:29,970 --> 00:02:31,290
[Episode 17]

3
00:03:01,500 --> 00:03:03,730
[Happiness]

4
00:03:07,630 --> 00:03:08,800
Why are you here?

5
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:13,160
Your Majesty.

6
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:14,360
What's wrong?

7
00:03:14,590 --> 00:03:15,400
Yingying.

8
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:18,220
Go back to the bedchamber and wait for me.

9
00:03:21,370 --> 00:03:23,340
[Happiness]

10
00:03:33,470 --> 00:03:34,280
Che.

11
00:03:38,030 --> 00:03:39,360
It's been over 10 years.

12
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:41,560
You've grown up.

13
00:03:42,310 --> 00:03:43,870
Mother, if you're here to reminisce,

14
00:03:43,870 --> 00:03:45,000
there's no need.

15
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:45,800
[Lingxi, Holy Maiden of the Yue State,
Jun Che's mother]

16
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:47,680
If you have come
as the representative of the envoys,

17
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:49,840
I have already received the gifts.

18
00:03:50,680 --> 00:03:53,470
Back then, I failed you as a mother.

19
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:57,360
Mother, please don't abandon me.

20
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:58,870
Take me with you, please.

21
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:03,710
Why?

22
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:04,840
Why?

23
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:06,520
The storybooks say

24
00:04:06,590 --> 00:04:08,750
all mothers love their children.

25
00:04:08,750 --> 00:04:10,560
Why have you never loved me?

26
00:04:11,950 --> 00:04:13,600
Look at those eyes of yours.

27
00:04:14,430 --> 00:04:15,960
So much like your father's.

28
00:04:16,430 --> 00:04:17,870
And your body,

29
00:04:18,040 --> 00:04:20,570
with half of it
running with his filthy blood.

30
00:04:20,950 --> 00:04:22,600
You don't deserve my love!

31
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:24,480
Mother!

32
00:04:25,190 --> 00:04:27,560
Then I'll give back to you
all the filthy blood

33
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:29,090
that runs in this half of me!

34
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:36,390
Mother!

35
00:04:37,270 --> 00:04:38,190
Mother!

36
00:04:40,159 --> 00:04:41,510
Don't go!

37
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:44,920
Does it still hurt

38
00:04:46,510 --> 00:04:47,480
right here?

39
00:04:53,159 --> 00:04:56,120
Years ago, when the secret guards
of the State of Yue rescued you

40
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:57,870
from the arena
and brought you back to the Yue State

41
00:04:57,870 --> 00:04:59,800
I was in seclusion,
recovering from my wounds.

42
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:01,160
I was too weak to see you.

43
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:04,630
But when I heard your wound
caused you pain day and night,

44
00:05:04,630 --> 00:05:06,290
I mixed my blood into medicine

45
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:08,070
to make this ointment for you.

46
00:05:11,370 --> 00:05:13,560
[Happiness]

47
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:16,430
Wait for you?

48
00:05:16,630 --> 00:05:17,800
I want to see

49
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:20,000
what reason you have for making me wait.

50
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:46,630
My empress, you're not
in our bedchamber late at night.

51
00:05:46,630 --> 00:05:48,310
Are you planning to flee our marriage?

52
00:05:48,310 --> 00:05:49,920
That depends on whether you're hiding

53
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:50,870
someone from me.

54
00:05:53,070 --> 00:05:54,950
I'm not ready for you to meet her yet.

55
00:05:54,950 --> 00:05:56,810
So you really are hiding someone?

56
00:05:57,510 --> 00:05:59,480
How dare you treat me
like this on our wedding night?

57
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:01,280
Perhaps I should kill you first,

58
00:06:01,310 --> 00:06:02,430
to spare myself

59
00:06:02,430 --> 00:06:05,490
the sight of all the other women
you favor in your harem.

60
00:06:06,190 --> 00:06:07,590
She's not a woman I favor,

61
00:06:08,190 --> 00:06:09,270
but a foe.

62
00:06:15,070 --> 00:06:17,390
She's your mother?

63
00:06:19,830 --> 00:06:21,120
In my previous life,
when I married into the palace,

64
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:22,750
his mother was already dead.

65
00:06:22,830 --> 00:06:24,360
I never thought in this life

66
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:26,160
I would see her alive.

67
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:26,920
Yingying.

68
00:06:28,270 --> 00:06:30,750
Do you think a mother
who didn't love her child

69
00:06:30,750 --> 00:06:32,610
can truly become a loving mother?

70
00:06:32,870 --> 00:06:34,159
She apologized to you,

71
00:06:34,159 --> 00:06:36,290
begging for your forgiveness, right?

72
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:38,659
Do you think I should forgive her?

73
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:44,850
Love that comes too late
is better left unwanted.

74
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:47,360
As expected of my wife.

75
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:49,360
We said the same thing.

76
00:06:54,950 --> 00:06:56,950
Can an ointment that's 15 years late

77
00:06:57,390 --> 00:06:59,480
heal old wounds?

78
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:01,510
Keeping this scar

79
00:07:01,870 --> 00:07:03,720
serves as a reminder to me

80
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:05,920
of what abandonment feels like.

81
00:07:08,830 --> 00:07:11,120
I understand your purpose in coming today.

82
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:12,160
You want to remind me

83
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:13,560
that Yue State saved me.

84
00:07:14,390 --> 00:07:16,450
Rest assured, I will keep my promise.

85
00:07:16,510 --> 00:07:18,040
Yue State helped me ascend the throne,

86
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:20,360
so I will integrate Yue State into Daning.

87
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:21,820
If you think of me this way,

88
00:07:22,510 --> 00:07:23,830
I don't blame you.

89
00:07:25,070 --> 00:07:26,680
But I truly don't want

90
00:07:26,870 --> 00:07:28,800
only hatred to remain between us.

91
00:07:29,310 --> 00:07:30,480
After all, in your body

92
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:32,210
flows blood that belongs to me,

93
00:07:32,510 --> 00:07:34,000
to Yue State.

94
00:07:34,630 --> 00:07:35,430
Back then,

95
00:07:36,159 --> 00:07:38,430
you abandoned me because I had

96
00:07:38,430 --> 00:07:40,270
Daning blood flowing in my veins.

97
00:07:40,270 --> 00:07:43,000
Now because of my other half bloodline,

98
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:45,560
you want to restore
our mother-son relationship.

99
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:46,310
Mother,

100
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:48,680
don't you find it ridiculous?

101
00:07:49,190 --> 00:07:50,000
Che.

102
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:53,510
According to the law, envoys

103
00:07:53,510 --> 00:07:55,240
cannot stay long in the palace.

104
00:07:55,510 --> 00:07:56,480
Please leave.

105
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:57,190
Che!

106
00:08:00,070 --> 00:08:00,920
Che!

107
00:08:01,830 --> 00:08:03,040
Do you remember this?

108
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:04,800
I took it away back then

109
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:07,490
just to keep something to remember you by.

110
00:08:07,750 --> 00:08:08,560
Now,

111
00:08:09,510 --> 00:08:11,710
it can finally return
to its true owner.

112
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:21,830
Do you like it?

113
00:08:25,920 --> 00:08:26,980
I'll play with you.

114
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:34,030
I am no longer a child.

115
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:35,650
I don't need it anymore.

116
00:08:36,150 --> 00:08:37,669
Che! Che!

117
00:08:39,150 --> 00:08:39,960
Actually,

118
00:08:40,549 --> 00:08:42,750
I only have 6 months left to live.

119
00:08:43,549 --> 00:08:45,600
I just want to

120
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:47,900
remember your face well before I die.

121
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:49,200
Che.

122
00:08:52,630 --> 00:08:53,440
Three days.

123
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:55,030
After 3 days,

124
00:08:55,150 --> 00:08:57,840
you will return
to Yue State with the other envoys.

125
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:58,630
Che!

126
00:08:58,630 --> 00:08:59,910
Che!

127
00:09:00,750 --> 00:09:01,480
Che.

128
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:10,510
It's okay.

129
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:12,850
I'll be by your side from now on.

130
00:09:21,670 --> 00:09:22,480
What...

131
00:09:22,790 --> 00:09:24,270
What are you doing?

132
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:27,420
Naturally, what married couples should do.

133
00:09:30,050 --> 00:09:32,170
[Happiness]

134
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:47,910
You just mentioned
the women I favor in the harem.

135
00:09:47,910 --> 00:09:49,630
To balance the power of all parties,

136
00:09:49,630 --> 00:09:50,830
taking many consorts

137
00:09:50,910 --> 00:09:52,510
is also an essential part.

138
00:09:52,750 --> 00:09:54,200
You're not allowed to have even one.

139
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:55,000
Otherwise...

140
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:01,670
How could someone make

141
00:10:01,670 --> 00:10:03,000
the same mistake twice?

142
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:21,270
Otherwise,

143
00:10:22,360 --> 00:10:23,820
you know what will happen.

144
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:26,200
You want to kill me?

145
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:27,150
♪ Spring arrives,
though snow still lingers ♪

146
00:10:27,150 --> 00:10:28,000
If you kill me,

147
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:30,360
you'll become a widow.

148
00:10:30,390 --> 00:10:30,530
Not at all.

149
00:10:30,530 --> 00:10:31,670
♪ After all the joys
and sorrows we've known ♪

150
00:10:31,670 --> 00:10:34,080
I'll build my own harem,

151
00:10:34,210 --> 00:10:34,480
♪ Our story drifts
through endless streets ♪

152
00:10:34,480 --> 00:10:36,440
fill a palace with male concubines,

153
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:38,150
and live a life of pleasure.

154
00:10:38,230 --> 00:10:40,760
♪ I turned away,
and lost you in the haze ♪

155
00:10:42,350 --> 00:10:45,380
♪ The past lies between our worlds ♪

156
00:10:46,190 --> 00:10:49,370
♪ When we meet again beneath the moon ♪

157
00:10:50,030 --> 00:10:52,910
♪ Will you be cold,
or will you still be mine? ♪

158
00:10:52,910 --> 00:10:53,550
You want to tame me like a wolf?

159
00:10:53,550 --> 00:10:55,550
♪ Among the crowd we brushed in passing ♪

160
00:10:55,550 --> 00:10:56,360
Too bad.

161
00:10:57,360 --> 00:10:58,820
I'm fiercer than any wolf.

162
00:10:59,710 --> 00:11:01,670
♪ But love kept burning through my soul ♪

163
00:11:01,670 --> 00:11:03,270
If you want male concubines,

164
00:11:03,750 --> 00:11:03,880
they must pass three tests.

165
00:11:03,880 --> 00:11:05,320
♪ Longing weaves its silent net ♪

166
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:06,380
Which three tests?

167
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:07,670
First,

168
00:11:07,960 --> 00:11:08,150
♪ I dare not speak, I dare not stare ♪

169
00:11:08,150 --> 00:11:09,550
strong enough to beat me.

170
00:11:10,720 --> 00:11:11,510
Second,

171
00:11:11,990 --> 00:11:12,150
♪ Still I'm drawn to your shining eyes ♪

172
00:11:12,150 --> 00:11:13,550
bring comfort to the bed.

173
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:15,320
And third...

174
00:11:15,320 --> 00:11:19,290
♪ Time has buried so much of us ♪

175
00:11:20,020 --> 00:11:20,790
♪ Splendor fades to quiet sorrow ♪

176
00:11:20,790 --> 00:11:22,150
endure this.

177
00:11:23,820 --> 00:11:24,720
♪ Only after tasting
all the world's illusions ♪

178
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:26,650
How do you know I can't handle this?

179
00:11:28,010 --> 00:11:30,220
♪ Could I kiss your face ♪

180
00:11:33,860 --> 00:11:37,190
♪ The past lies between our worlds ♪

181
00:11:37,760 --> 00:11:40,830
♪ When we meet again beneath the moon ♪

182
00:11:41,570 --> 00:11:45,150
♪ Will you be cold,
or will you still be mine? ♪

183
00:11:45,600 --> 00:11:49,660
♪ Among the crowd we brushed in passing ♪

184
00:12:03,630 --> 00:12:04,910
Five.

185
00:12:05,870 --> 00:12:07,670
Yan Hui.
